        "text_QJAmND": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Wave's range of kayaks has something for everyone - whether you're looking to kick back on calm waters or ride the tides. Riding with friends? No problem, we can sit up to three! We have a range of kayaks to suit any budget and skill level.</p><p>Throughout history, kayaks have been used as a means of transport, but we're mainly interested in having fun on the water! Wave's range of kayaks has something for everyone - whether you're looking to kick back on calm waters or ride the tides. Riding with friends? No problem, we can sit up to three!</p><p>All of our kayaks come with everything you need to get on the water and pack down into their carry bags for easy transportation and storage. <br/><br/></p>",
